==年代爭議==
齒河盜龍的標本採集自{{link-en|帕里艾克層|Pari Aike Formation}}，現時分別被不同研究認為屬於{{link-en|黃灌木層|Mata Amarilla Formation}}中段<ref name="varelaetal2012"/>或別稱為{{link-en|丘堡層|Cerro Fortaleza Formation}}。<ref>{{cite journal |author1=Elena R. Schroeter |author2=Victoria M. Egerton |author3=Lucio M. Ibiricu |author4=Kenneth J. Lacovara | year = 2014 | title=Lamniform Shark Teeth from the Late Cretaceous of Southernmost South America (Santa Cruz Province, Argentina) | journal =PLOS ONE | volume =9 | issue=8 | pages =e104800 | doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0104800 | pmid=25141301 | pmc=4139311|bibcode=2014PLoSO...9j4800S |doi-access=free }}</ref><ref name="Lacovara et al., 2014">{{cite journal|author1=Kenneth J. Lacovara |author2=Matthew C. Lamanna |author3=Lucio M. Ibiricu |author4=Jason C. Poole |author5=Elena R. Schroeter |author6=Paul V. Ullmann |author7=Kristyn K. Voegele |author8=Zachary M. Boles |author9=Aja M. Carter |author10=Emma K. Fowler |author11=Victoria M. Egerton |author12=Alison E. Moyer |author13=Christopher L. Coughenour |author14=Jason P. Schein |author15=Jerald D. Harris |author16=Rubén D. Martínez |author17=Fernando E. Novas |title=A Gigantic, Exceptionally Complete Titanosaurian Sauropod Dinosaur from Southern Patagonia, Argentina (Supplementary information)|journal=Scientific Reports|year=2014|doi=10.1038/srep06196 |pmid=25186586 |volume=4 |pages=6196 |pmc=5385829|bibcode=2014NatSR...4E6196L }}</ref>起初鑑定年代為[[馬斯垂克階|馬斯垂克階]]，於是成為最年輕的大盜龍類。但較近期研究則將年代提前至[[森諾曼階|森諾曼階]]至[[桑托階|桑托階]]。<ref name="varelaetal2012"/><ref name="novasetal2013">{{cite journal | last1 = Novas| first1 = F. E. | last2 = Agnolín | first2 = F. L. | last3 = Ezcurra | first3 = M. D. | last4 = Porfiri | first4 = J. | last5 = Canale | first5 = J. I. | year = 2013 | title = Evolution of the carnivorous dinosaurs during the Cretaceous: The evidence from Patagonia | journal =Cretaceous Research | volume = 45 |pages=174–215 | doi =  10.1016/j.cretres.2013.04.001}}</ref>黃灌木層中段保存了距今9620萬±70萬年前的森諾曼階凝灰岩層。<ref name="varelaetal2012">{{cite journal | last1 = Varela | first1 = A. N. | last2 = Poiré | first2 = D. G. | last3 = Martin | first3 = T. | last4 = Gerdes | first4 = A. | last5 = Goin | first5 = F. J. | last6 = Gelfo | first6 = J. N. | last7 = Hoffmann | first7 = S. | year = 2012 | title = U-Pb zircon constraints on the age of the Cretaceous Mata Amarilla Formation, Southern Patagonia, Argentina: Its relationship with the evolution of the Austral Basin | journal = Andean Geology | volume = 39 | issue = 3 | pages = 359–379 | doi = 10.5027/andgeoV39n3-a01 | doi-access = free }}</ref>但齒河盜龍來自的Cerro Hornos遺址在近期研究被認為年代落在[[坎潘階|坎潘階]]，約7600萬至7000萬年前。<ref>{{Cite journal|last1=Sickmann|first1=Zachary T.|last2=Schwartz|first2=Theresa M.|last3=Graham|first3=Stephan A.|date=2018|title=Refining stratigraphy and tectonic history using detrital zircon maximum depositional age: an example from the Cerro Fortaleza Formation, Austral Basin, southern Patagonia|journal=Basin Research|language=en|volume=30|issue=4|pages=708–729|doi=10.1111/bre.12272|doi-access=free}}</ref>這與2022年[[颸戮龍|颸戮龍]]的發表提到在晚白堊世後段南半球大盜龍類出現體型巨大化的時間點相符，而當時已知大盜龍類的分布皆集中於岡瓦那大陸最南端，其中亦包括齒河盜龍。<ref name=maip>{{Cite journal |last=Rolando |first=Alexis M. A. |last2=Motta |first2=Matias J. |last3=Agnolín |first3=Federico L. |last4=Manabe |first4=Makoto |last5=Tsuihiji |first5=Takanobu |last6=Novas |first6=Fernando E. |date=2022-04-26 |title=A large Megaraptoridae (Theropoda: Coelurosauria) from Upper Cretaceous (Maastrichtian) of Patagonia, Argentina |url=https://www.nature.com/articles/s41598-022-09272-z |journal=Scientific Reports |volume=12 |issue=1 |pages=Article number 6318 |doi=10.1038/s41598-022-09272-z |doi-access=free}}</ref>

